0.text: Innate: Tahm Kench's basic attacks and  Tongue Lash deal 12 − 60 (based on level) (+ 2.5% of his bonus health) bonus magic damage.

1.text: Passive: Basic attacks and  Tongue Lash against enemy  champions apply An Acquired Taste stack for 5 seconds, stacking up to 3 times, with the duration refreshing on  Tongue Lash and subsequent attacks. The stacks decay once every 0.67 seconds when the duration ends.

2.text: Tongue Lash and  Devour gain additional effects against enemies with 3 stacks.

0.text: Active: Tahm Kench lashes his tongue in the target direction, dealing magic damage to the first enemy hit and  slowing them by 40% for 2 seconds, as well as  healing himself if an enemy champion is hit.

1.text: If an enemy champion is struck while at three  An Acquired Taste stacks, all of their stacks are consumed to  stun them for 1.5 seconds.

2.text: During Tongue Lash,  Devour can be cast at no cost to swallow the target enemy champion hit while at 3  An Acquired Taste stacks after pulling them towards him.

3.text: Tongue Lash's range and travel speed can be increased by Tahm Kench's size.

0.text: Active: Tahm Kench dives into the waters,  channeling for 1.35 seconds and upon completion  blinking to the target location, emerging after a 0.15-second delay and remaining  unable to act for 0.65 seconds after the channel completes.

1.text: Upon emerging from the depths, Tahm Kench deals magic damage to nearby enemies and  knocks them up and  stuns them for 1 second. If Abyssal Dive hits at least one enemy  champion, 40% of its  cooldown and  mana cost are refunded.

2.text: Enemies can see the indicator for Tahm Kench's destination after he has channeled for 0.75 seconds. Tahm Kench grants  sight of the area during the channel.

0.text: Passive: Tahm Kench stores a percentage of the post-mitigation damage he takes as grey health on his health bar, up to a maximum of 300% of his maximum health.

1.text: While Thick Skin is available, and after taking no damage for 4 seconds, Tahm Kench rapidly  heals himself to restore 30% − 100% (based on level) of his grey health. Every 0.264 seconds he heals for 10% of his maximum health.

2.text: Active: Tahm Kench converts his current grey health into a  shield that lasts for 2.5 seconds.

0.text: Active: Tahm Kench swallows the target  champion for up to 3 seconds, rendering them  vanished and  unable to act, as well as granting them  displacement immunity for the duration.

1.text: If the target is an ally, they are granted a  shield for 2.5 seconds, refreshing after they are  Regurgitated. Tahm Kench is  slowed and unable to cast movement spells, excluding  Abyssal Dive, while an ally is swallowed.

2.text: If the target is an enemy, they are  suppressed for the duration. Devour can only be cast on enemies with 3  An Acquired Taste stacks, consuming them in the process. Tahm Kench is  grounded and  slowed by 40% while an enemy is swallowed.

3.text: After 1 second, Devour can be recast into  Regurgitate while Tahm Kench's belly is full, and automatically does so at the end of the duration if they are still so. Allied champions can exit at will by inputting a movement command after the same delay, unless they're  immobilized.

4.text: If Tahm Kench is performing  Abyssal Dive,  Regurgitate will not automatically cast until after he finishes.

0.text: Active: Tahm Kench  spits the target out in the target direction. If the target is an enemy, they are dealt magic damage at the end of the displacement.
